sense.  Each word of memory for the VC1620 was supposed to be 12 digits. =
 There is no reason to assume that it cannot hold numbers of this size.  =
The only numbers that are 5 digits are addresses.  The 12 digit limit is =
clearly stated on the first line of the description of the VC 1620.  See =
the link: =
https://pages.ramapo.edu/~vmiller/SoftwareDesign/VC1620Spec.htm

